data.description: Are you searching for a home that needs love and you can call your own?  Well, search no further!  4818 Mitchells Ridge is the perfect home for you! This traditional  4 bedroom 2.5 bath home is awaiting your special touch!!  With separate dining room, living room, family room with gas starter fireplace, and eat-in-kitchen with bar area, you already have a nice entertaining space for your gatherings.  Upstairs you'll find a huge owners suite with double sinks, soaking tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. 3 additional nice sized bedrooms, hall bathroom and laundry.  2-car garage and large beautifully maintained lot.  The community is BEAUTIFUL. MUST SEE!  5 min to I-675, shopping and Marta! 5 min to Fairview Community. Home will need renovation loan for rehab.  OPEN TO ALL INVESTORS.  Seller is very motivated.
